'''腹腔'''（英語：abdominal cavity）是[[人类|人类]]和许多[[动物|动物]]身上的一个體積龐大的[[体腔|体腔]]<ref name=EB>{{cite encyclopedia|encyclopedia=Encyclopædia Britannica|title=Abdominal cavity|edition=15th|year=2010|publisher=Encyclopædia Britannica, Inc.|volume=I: A-Ak – Bayes|location=Chicago, Illinois|isbn=978-1-59339-837-8|pages=[https://archive.org/details/newencyclopaedia2009ency/page/19 19–20]|url-access=registration|url=https://archive.org/details/newencyclopaedia2009ency/page/19}}</ref>，內有许多器官。它是{{link-en|腹盆腔|Abdominopelvic cavity}}的一部分<ref name="Wingerd">{{Cite book|last=Wingerd|first=Bruce|title=The Human Body: Concepts of Anatomy and Physiology|url=https://archive.org/details/humanbodyconcept0000wing|publisher=Saunders College Publishing|year=1994|location=Fort Worth|pages=[https://archive.org/details/humanbodyconcept0000wing/page/11 11]–12|isbn=0-03-055507-8}}</ref>，位于[[胸腔|胸腔]]的下方和{{link-en|盆腔|Pelvic cavity}}的上方。它的圆顶状的顶部是[[橫膈膜|橫膈膜]]，是[[肺部|肺部]]下面的一片薄薄的[[肌肉|肌肉]]，腹腔的底部是与[[骨盆|骨盆]]相通的{{link-en|骨盆入口|Pelvic inlet}}。

